ing: 1/4 cup frozen blackberries, or to taste
des: "Wonderful for on-the-go and filling, but not too filling."
ins: Blend fresh pineapple, dates, and vanilla extract together in a Vitamix(R) or blender until smooth, about 90 seconds. Add blackberries and blend, about 90 seconds. Add kale and blend, about 90 seconds; repeat for 90 seconds more. Add frozen pineapple and blend until smooth, about 90 seconds.
